ilon ] the\nresulting measure on \\sigma'. The measure \\mu_j^n[\\nu,\\epsilon ] is a\nperturbation of the measure \\mu_j^n.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 2004 03:51:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2005 12:44:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-06-13"}
