tions, a general structure theorem and the handle sliding lemma of Novikov\nFloer cycles over such a family and a {\\it family version} of new\ntransversality statements involving the Floer chain map, and many others. We\ncall this chain level Floer theory as a whole the {\\it Floer mini-max theory}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 2004 05:09:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Jul 2004 01:15:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2007 09:38:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 6 Sep 2007 01:27:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-03-14"}
